WITH "cte" AS (SELECT DISTINCT "student_id","course_id","grade",DENSE_RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY "student_id" ORDER BY "grade" DESC,"course_id") AS "rk" FROM "Enrollments") SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade" FROM "cte" WHERE "rk"=1 ORDER BY "student_id"

SELECT "t1"."student_id",MIN("t1"."course_id") AS "course_id","t1"."grade" FROM (SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade",MAX("grade") OVER (PARTITION BY "student_id") AS "Max_grade" FROM "Enrollments") AS "t1" WHERE "t1"."grade"="t1"."Max_grade" GROUP BY "t1"."student_id" ORDER BY "t1"."student_id"

WITH "t" AS (SELECT "student_id",MAX("grade") AS "max_g" FROM "enrollments" GROUP BY "student_id") SELECT "e"."student_id" AS "student_id",MIN("course_id") AS "course_id","e"."grade" AS "grade" FROM "enrollments" AS "e" JOIN "t" ON "e"."student_id"="t"."student_id" AND "e"."grade"="t"."max_g" GROUP BY "student_id","grade" ORDER BY "student_id"

WITH "TEMP" AS (SELECT "STUDENT_ID","COURSE_ID","GRADE",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY "STUDENT_ID" ORDER BY "GRADE" DESC,"COURSE_ID") AS "RNK" FROM "ENROLLMENTS") SELECT "STUDENT_ID","COURSE_ID","GRADE" FROM "TEMP" WHERE "RNK"=1 ORDER BY 1

SELECT "student_id",MIN("course_id") AS "course_id","grade" FROM "enrollments" WHERE ROW("student_id","grade") IN (SELECT "student_id",MAX("grade") AS "grade" FROM "enrollments" GROUP BY "student_id") GROUP BY "student_id" ORDER BY "student_id"

SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade" FROM (SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY "student_id" ORDER BY "grade" DESC,"course_id") AS "rnk" FROM "Enrollments") AS "t" WHERE "rnk"=1
SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade" FROM (SELECT *,DENSE_RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY "student_id" ORDER BY "grade" DESC,"course_id") AS "rnk" FROM "Enrollments") AS "cte" WHERE "rnk"=1

WITH "base" AS (SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade",ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "student_id" ORDER BY "grade" DESC,"course_id") AS "seq" FROM "Enrollments" ORDER BY 1) SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade" FROM "base" WHERE "seq"=1 ORDER BY 1

SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade" FROM (SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade",ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "student_id" ORDER BY "grade" DESC,"course_id") AS "rnk" FROM "enrollments") AS "a" WHERE "rnk"=1 ORDER BY "student_id"

WITH "high_grade" AS (SELECT "student_id",MAX("grade") AS "grade" FROM "Enrollments" GROUP BY "student_id") SELECT "H"."student_id",MIN("E"."course_id") AS "course_id","H"."grade" FROM "Enrollments" AS "E" JOIN "high_grade" AS "H" ON "E"."student_id"="H"."student_id" AND "H"."grade"="E"."grade" GROUP BY "H"."student_id","H"."grade" ORDER BY "student_id"
SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade" FROM (SELECT *,DENSE_RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY "student_id" ORDER BY "grade" DESC,"course_id") AS "rnk" FROM "Enrollments") AS "a" WHERE "a"."rnk"=1

SELECT "a"."student_id","a"."course_id","a"."grade" FROM (SELECT *,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "student_id" ORDER BY "grade" DESC,"course_id") AS "r" FROM "Enrollments") AS "a" WHERE "r"=1 ORDER BY "student_id"

WITH "comp" AS (SELECT *,RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY "student_id" ORDER BY "grade" DESC,"course_id") AS "rnk" FROM "Enrollments" ORDER BY "student_id") SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade" FROM "comp" WHERE "rnk"=1

SELECT "y"."student_id","y"."course_id","y"."grade" FROM (SELECT "x"."student_id","x"."course_id","x"."grade",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY "x"."student_id" ORDER BY "x"."course_id") AS "rank_course" FROM (SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY "student_id" ORDER BY "grade" DESC) AS "rank_grade" FROM "Enrollments") AS "x" WHERE "x"."rank_grade"=1) AS "y" WHERE "y"."rank_course"=1

SELECT "student_id",MIN("course_id") AS "course_id","grade" FROM (SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY "student_id" ORDER BY "grade" DESC) AS "rnk" FROM "Enrollments") AS "a" WHERE "rnk"=1 GROUP BY "student_id" ORDER BY "student_id"

WITH "new" AS (SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade",ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "student_id" ORDER BY "grade" DESC,"course_id") AS "row_num" FROM "enrollments") SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade" FROM "new" WHERE "row_num"=1 ORDER BY "student_id"

SELECT "student_id",MIN("course_id") AS "course_id","grade" FROM "Enrollments" WHERE ROW("student_id","grade") IN (SELECT "student_id",MAX("grade") FROM "Enrollments" GROUP BY 1) GROUP BY 1,3 ORDER BY 1

SELECT "student_id",MIN("course_id") AS "course_id","grade" FROM "enrollments" WHERE ROW("student_id","grade") IN (SELECT "student_id",MAX("grade") AS "max_grade" FROM "enrollments" GROUP BY 1) GROUP BY 1 ORDER BY 1

SELECT "q"."student_id",MIN("q"."course_id") AS "course_id","q"."grade" FROM "Enrollments" AS "q" WHERE ROW("q"."student_id","q"."grade") IN (SELECT "student_id",MAX("grade") AS "grade" FROM "Enrollments" GROUP BY "student_id") GROUP BY "student_id","grade" ORDER BY "student_id"

SELECT "c"."student_id","c"."course_id","c"."grade" FROM (SELECT "e"."student_id","e"."course_id","e"."grade",ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY "e"."student_id" ORDER BY "e"."course_id") AS "row_num" FROM "enrollments" AS "e" JOIN (SELECT "student_id",MAX("grade") AS "grade" FROM "enrollments" AS "e" GROUP BY "student_id") AS "b" ON "e"."student_id"="b"."student_id" AND "e"."grade"="b"."grade") AS "c" WHERE "row_num"=1

SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade" FROM (SELECT "student_id",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY "student_id" ORDER BY "grade" DESC,"course_id") AS "rn","course_id","grade" FROM "Enrollments") AS "t1" WHERE "t1"."rn"=1 ORDER BY "student_id"

WITH "t1" AS (SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY "student_id" ORDER BY "grade" DESC) AS "rn" FROM "enrollments") SELECT "student_id",MIN("course_id") AS "course_id","grade" FROM "t1" WHERE "rn"=1 GROUP BY 1

WITH "cte" AS (SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade",RANK() OVER (PARTITION BY "student_id" ORDER BY "grade" DESC,"course_id") AS "rank1" FROM "Enrollments") SELECT "student_id","course_id","grade" FROM "cte" WHERE "rank1"=1 ORDER BY "student_id"
